text: Camilla Rosatello (born 28 May 1995) is an Italian tennis player. She has a career-high singles ranking of world No. 225, achieved on 7 August 2017. On 29 January 2018, she peaked at No. 134 in the doubles rankings. Rosatello has won 23 ITF doubles titles. On the junior tour, she had a career-high ranking of 30, achieved in January 2013.
